  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/f49b7660d1b03d78be99c6efbd6666cf.poster.avif?t=1757757169\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/f49b7660d1b03d78be99c6efbd6666cf.webm?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/f49b7660d1b03d78be99c6efbd6666cf.mp4?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is a fireworks event in the evening and your friend knows just the right place to watch it. All you have to do is get there through this perfectly normal park. Just follow the arrows and you'll reach your destination. Eventually. How hard can that be? And what number of acorns is enough acorns?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic platformer experience<br></li><li>Simple controls<br></li><li>Grumpy bosses<br></li><li>Reach your destination as fast as possible<br></li><li>And don't forget to drink your water!</li></ul><br>Accessibility<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Change controls at any point in game<br></li><li>Customize color rendering and reduce motion</li></ul><br>A couple tips before you go<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Look around! This is no ordinary park. There might be hidden secrets...<br></li><li>Practice makes perfect. You can do it!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/a73cbf1eaacc1667eee60c0b46801bac.poster.avif?t=1757757169\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/a73cbf1eaacc1667eee60c0b46801bac.webm?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/a73cbf1eaacc1667eee60c0b46801bac.mp4?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/f49b7660d1b03d78be99c6efbd6666cf.poster.avif?t=1757757169\" width=600 height=80 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/f49b7660d1b03d78be99c6efbd6666cf.webm?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/f49b7660d1b03d78be99c6efbd6666cf.mp4?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There is a fireworks event in the evening and your friend knows just the right place to watch it. All you have to do is get there through this perfectly normal park. Just follow the arrows and you'll reach your destination. Eventually. How hard can that be? And what number of acorns is enough acorns?<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classic platformer experience<br></li><li>Simple controls<br></li><li>Grumpy bosses<br></li><li>Reach your destination as fast as possible<br></li><li>And don't forget to drink your water!</li></ul><br>Accessibility<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Change controls at any point in game<br></li><li>Customize color rendering and reduce motion</li></ul><br>A couple tips before you go<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Look around! This is no ordinary park. There might be hidden secrets...<br></li><li>Practice makes perfect. You can do it!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/a73cbf1eaacc1667eee60c0b46801bac.poster.avif?t=1757757169\" width=600 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/a73cbf1eaacc1667eee60c0b46801bac.webm?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2560020/extras/a73cbf1eaacc1667eee60c0b46801bac.mp4?t=1757757169\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
